  "title": "Field Service Engineer – Epson Products",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role & Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Troubleshoot, repair, and maintain <u>Epson</u> carry-in products (Copiers, Printers), mainly projectors</p></li><li><p>Travel to customers’ locations to provide on-site service and support when needed</p></li><li><p>Proactively interact with customers to explain services and provide technical guidance</p></li><li>Handle all essential tools, materials, and equipment for efficient and effective service delivery</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Key Competencies</strong><br />•\tGood level of customer service experience.<br />•\tGood communication skills to enable interaction with internal and external customers.<br /><br /><strong>Qualification:</strong><br />•\tNITEC/ Diploma in Engineering/Electrical/Mechanical/Computer-related or equivalent discipline.<br />•\tCandidates without prior working experience are also welcome - \"on-the-job training\" will be provided.<br />•\tPossess own Motorbike w/ valid Singapore Class 2B driving License \"preferred\".<br /><br /><strong>Benefits:</strong><br />•\tLearning culture where every employee is engaged in learning and development growth.<br />•\tTeam programs and activities that celebrate individual and team’s success.<br />•\tLong service award recognition for our committed and dedicated colleagues.<br />•\tMedical / Dental benefits cater for the employee’s health and wellness.<br /></p><p><strong>Workplace:</strong> near Tai Seng MRT</p>",
